            "text": "<p>BIRETIX is an innovative skincare range from Cantabria Labs, designed to meet the growing demand for effective, science-led solutions for blemish-prone and acne-prone skin. Combining RETINSPHERE® Technology, BIOPEP-15 and clinically proven dermatological actives, BIRETIX helps target the key factors associated with blemish-prone skin while supporting the skin barrier. Offering solutions for prevention, treatment support and maintenance, BIRETIX provides clinics, pharmacies and specialist skincare retailers with a trusted range that delivers visible results and encourages long-term customer loyalty. </p>"
